---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import ResumeLightbox from '../../components/ResumeLightbox.astro';

const BASE_URL = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="The Connector Hub | Amber Gianvecchio">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <article class="case-study">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="case-hero">
        <div class="container">
          <a href={`${BASE_URL}`} class="back-link">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M10 12L6 8L10 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
          <div class="hero-layout">
            <div class="hero-main">
              <h1>The Connector Hub</h1>
              <p class="case-subtitle">A centralized Notion workspace that eliminated cross-department bottlenecks at a remote-first company</p>
              <div class="case-meta">
                <div class="meta-item">
                  <span class="meta-label">Role</span>
                  <span class="meta-value">Senior Patient Onboarding Coordinator</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                  <span class="meta-label">Company</span>
                  <span class="meta-value">Advekit</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                  <span class="meta-label">Impact</span>
                  <span class="meta-value">Same-day response times</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="company-context-box">
              <img src={`${BASE_URL}images/advekit-logo.svg`} alt="Advekit logo" class="context-logo" />
              <p>Advekit makes therapy more accessible by taking insurance off people's plates. They match clients with therapists and manage all the billing, so people can focus on their mental health instead of fighting with their insurance company.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Content -->
      <section class="case-content">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>The Problem</h2>
            <p>
              As a remote-first company, we faced significant bottlenecks between departments. Teams were dependent on Slack responses that could take days, with Customer Success and Billing impacted the mostâ€”delays that then rippled out to engineering and product.
            </p>
            <p>
              We needed client information accessible in real time: trackable, editable, and visible to all departments so everyone could work from the same data.
            </p>

            <h2>What I Built</h2>
            <p>
              I spotted the inefficiency and pitched a solution to my manager, who gave me the go-ahead to build it out during my spare time.
            </p>
            <p>
              The Notion workspace centralized the information teams were constantly requesting from each other:
            </p>

            <!-- Hub Diagram - Sitemap Style -->
            <div class="hub-sitemap">
              <!-- Top: Connector Hub -->
              <div class="hub-top">
                <div class="hub-main">Connector Hub</div>
              </div>

              <!-- Connector lines -->
              <div class="hub-connectors">
                <div class="connector-line"></div>
                <div class="connector-line"></div>
                <div class="connector-line"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- Bottom: Three departments with their data -->
              <div class="hub-departments">
                <div class="dept-column">
                  <div class="dept-header">Sales</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Provider profiles & IDs</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">NPI & network status</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Region & clients</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Onboarding status</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Meeting notes</div>
                </div>
                <div class="dept-column">
                  <div class="dept-header">Customer Success</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Client profiles & IDs</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Insurance & SCAs</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Provider match</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Benefits info</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">HIPAA data (DOB, SSN)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="dept-column">
                  <div class="dept-header">Billing</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Claims status</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">SCA status</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Auth forms</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Charges & refunds</div>
                  <div class="dept-item">Consultant notes</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2>The Impact</h2>
            <p>
              Customer support messages started getting resolved within a day. Billing could access the information they needed independently, without waiting on my team.
            </p>
            <p>
              The cross-department Slack back-and-forth that used to consume hours each day was eliminated. Teams could move faster when they weren't blocked waiting for data, leading to measurable improvements in client retention and sales revenue.
            </p>

            <h2>Technologies</h2>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span class="tech-tag">Notion</span>
              <span class="tech-tag">Operations</span>
              <span class="tech-tag">Process Design</span>
              <span class="tech-tag">Remote Collaboration</span>
            </div>

            <a href={`${BASE_URL}`} class="back-link back-link-bottom">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M10 12L6 8L10 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
              Back to Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <ResumeLightbox />
</Layout>

<style>
  .case-study {
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .case-hero {
    padding: 60px 0 40px;
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .case-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-layout {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 60px;
  }

  .hero-main {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .company-context-box {
    width: 320px;
    padding: 24px;
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
    border-radius: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .context-logo {
    width: 120px;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .company-context-box p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .case-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .case-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .case-content {
    padding: 60px 0 80px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .tech-tag {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .back-link-bottom {
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Hub Sitemap Styles */
  .hub-sitemap {
    margin: 48px auto;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hub-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hub-main {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hub-connectors {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    height: 40px;
  }

  /* Vertical line from hub down */
  .hub-connectors::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    width: 2px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: var(--border);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  /* Horizontal line across */
  .hub-connectors::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 50px;
    right: 50px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--border);
  }

  .connector-line {
    position: absolute;
    width: 2px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: var(--border);
    top: 20px;
  }

  .connector-line:nth-child(1) {
    left: 50px;
  }

  .connector-line:nth-child(2) {
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .connector-line:nth-child(3) {
    right: 50px;
  }

  .hub-departments {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .dept-column {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .dept-header {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dept-item {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dept-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .case-hero {
      padding: 32px 0 24px;
    }

    .company-context-box {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .case-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .case-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .case-meta {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .content-wrapper h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    /* Mobile hub sitemap - fit without scaling */
    .hub-sitemap {
      margin: 32px auto;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .hub-main {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 10px 16px;
    }

    .hub-departments {
      gap: 8px;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    }

    .dept-column {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: subgrid;
      grid-row: span 2;
    }

    .dept-header {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      padding: 8px 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .dept-item {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      padding: 6px 6px;
    }

    .hub-connectors::after {
      left: 30px;
      right: 30px;
    }

    .connector-line:nth-child(1) {
      left: 30px;
    }

    .connector-line:nth-child(3) {
      right: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
